        <li><a href="/calculator/ideal-weight/">Ideal Weight Calculator</a> — Healthy weight range for your height using multiple formulas</li>
        <li><a href="/calculator/body-fat/">Body Fat Calculator</a> — Estimate body fat percentage from measurements</li>
        <li><a href="/calculator/macro/">Macro Calculator</a> — Optimal protein, carbs, and fat for your goals</li>
        <li><a href="/calculator/water-intake/">Water Intake Calculator</a> — Daily hydration target based on weight</li>
        <li><a href="/calculator/calorie/">Calorie Calculator</a> — Find calories needed for weight management</li>
        <li><a href="/calculator/age/">Age Calculator</a> — Your exact age for health screening benchmarks</li>
        <li><a href="/calculator/period-ovulation/">Period &amp; Ovulation Calculator</a> — BMI affects cycle regularity</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="related bmi-related-guides-block">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Related Guides</h2>
      <ul class="bmi-related-links">
        <li><a href="/blog/how-to-calculate-bmi/">How to Calculate BMI: Complete Guide with Indian Ranges</a></li>
        <li><a href="/blog/how-many-calories-per-day/">How Many Calories Per Day (Indian Food Chart)</a></li>
        <li><a href="/blog/how-much-water-per-day/">How Much Water Should You Drink Per Day?</a></li>
        <li><a href="/blog/how-to-track-period-cycle/">How to Track Your Period Cycle</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
